        <name>bt_bap_unicast_server_register_cb</name>
        <param>
          <type>const struct <ref refid="structbt__bap__unicast__server__cb" kindref="compound">bt_bap_unicast_server_cb</ref> *</type>
          <declname>cb</declname>
        </param>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Register unicast server callbacks. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Only one callback structure can be registered, and attempting to registering more than one will result in an error. Prior to calling this function the Unicast Server needs to be registered with <ref refid="group__bt__bap__unicast__server_1gab3ea6014854e6290f058c87e866c3191" kindref="member">bt_bap_unicast_server_register()</ref>.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>cb</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Unicast server callback structure.</para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para>0 in case of success or negative value in case of error. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
        <inbodydescription>
        </inbodydescription>
